messages.subject: Planning Deadlines
messages.msgSnippet: Another reminder on some conference offerings:    6 August         Hotel Reservations with conference rate.   After this date, the rate goes up considerably.
messages.messageBody:
Another reminder on some conference offerings: 

 
6 August Hotel Reservations with conference rate. After this
date, the rate goes up considerably. I'll not be able to do anything
about
the increase after this date! Get your room
booked in time! 
 
10 August Late Registration for the conference. After Aug 10,
"At the Door" prices are in effect. No exceptions! 
 
10 August T-Shirt Order deadline. I'll be ordering a very few
extras, but don't count on there being one for you if you don't pre-

order. 
   
10 August Banquet Reservations. We'll need your reservations and
payment for the Banquet by this time. 
 

Hope this helps with your planning! 
 

Kelly

ROOM UPDATE:
 
Rooms are dwindling. We have 16 rooms left for Wed-Sat (6-9 Sep); we
have 14 rooms left for Tues and Sun (5 and 10 Sep). 6 August is the
deadline for the group rate.
 
Once again, if I've missed an e-list in your state, area, etc., please
forward this on. 
 
Thanks to everyone- 
 
Ben Lovejoy 
Hotel Coordinator

messages.msgSnippet: Everyone-      Another update on rooms for our conference together in Albuquerque. We have rooms available -- some even on the main nights (Wed-Sat, 6-9
messages.messageBody:
Everyone- 
 
 
Another update on rooms for our conference together in Albuquerque. We
have rooms available -- some even on the main nights (Wed-Sat, 6-9
Sep). As of Tuesday, we were down 24 (of 169) rooms left on each of
those days. 6 August is our deadline with the hotel for the group rate;
we have 24 days from today to make reservations with that group rate.
Again, even if you're not sure if you're coming, make reservations to
ensure the conference group rate; you can always cancel the reservation.
 
One other thing: if I've missed an e-list in your state, area, etc.,
please forward this on. 
 
Thanks to all- 
 
Ben Lovejoy 
Hotel Coordinator

messages.subject: L&L Hotel Rooms
messages.msgSnippet: Everyone- Hope you all had a great 4th and are looking forward to a great July. Just sending out an update on rooms for our conference together in Albuquerque.
messages.messageBody:
Everyone-

Hope you all had a great 4th and are looking forward to a great July.

Just sending out an update on rooms for our conference together in
Albuquerque. We still rooms available, but we'e getting close to
running out of rooms on the conference nights (Wed-Sun, 6-9 Sep). As
of today, we have 28 rooms left on each of those days. While this may
seem like plenty, we've already made reservations for 141 rooms for
each of those nights. With the 6 August deadline for the group rate
coming in 32 days from today, this e-mail is to remind those who
haven't made reservations to do so. Even if you're not sure if you're
coming, I'd make the reservation to ensure the conference group rate;
you can always cancel the reservation. I'll send out several more
e-mails before the deadline date.

One other thing: if I've missed an e-list in your state, area, etc.,
please forward this on.

Thanks to everyone-

Ben Lovejoy
Hotel Coordinator
